title: Market share of leading insurance companies in Belgium 2015 to 2018
summary: This grouped bar chart shows Market share on the Y-axis for 18 different Insurance Companys for 4 groups 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018 that are presented on the X-axis.
Out of all 4 groups, 2016 had the highest Market share for Insurance Company AG Insurance and 2015 had the lowest Market share for Insurance Company Foyer.
The maximum Market share for 2018 that was found in Insurance Company AG Insurance was 0 times larger than the minimum Market share observed in Insurance Company Delta Lloyd.
Averaging all 4 groups 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018, the Insurance Company AG Insurance is the maximum Market share and Foyer is the minimum Market share.
